  {a:'NVDA', b:'AI-capex', v:1, sg:1, ch:'Bellwether of the AI-accelerator capex trade; the stock IS the AI-capex narrative (record $589B 1-day loss on the DeepSeek capex-doubt shock).', src:'public'},
